<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Artjunks</title>
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1rem;
        }
        h1 {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            padding: 2rem 0;
        }
        .card {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
        .card-content {
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        p {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .card-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }
        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #2980b9;
        }
    </style>

    
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>About Artjunks</h1>
        <p>Where creativity meets opportunity</p>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="grid">
            <div class="card">
                <img src="/api/placeholder/400/200" alt="Artjunks Community" class="card-image">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h2>Our Story</h2>
                    <p>Artjunks is a vibrant community marketplace where creativity meets opportunity. Founded in [year], we've made it our mission to connect talented artists with art enthusiasts around the world.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <img src="/api/placeholder/400/200" alt="Artist Showcase" class="card-image">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h2>Our Vision</h2>
                    <p>At Artjunks, we believe that art has the power to transform spaces, spark conversations, and enrich lives. We envision a world where every artist has a platform to showcase their unique vision, and every art lover can discover pieces that speak to their soul.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <img src="/api/placeholder/400/200" alt="Art Marketplace" class="card-image">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h2>What We Do</h2>
                    <p>We provide a user-friendly online platform where artists can set up digital storefronts, art enthusiasts can browse diverse collections, and buyers and sellers can interact directly, fostering a sense of community and personal connection.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <img src="/api/placeholder/400/200" alt="Quality Assurance" class="card-image">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
                    <p>Quality and authenticity are at the heart of everything we do. We carefully vet our artists to ensure that every piece on Artjunks is original and of high quality. We're committed to fair practices, ensuring that artists receive the majority of the proceeds from their sales.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <img src="/api/placeholder/400/200" alt="Artjunks Team" class="card-image">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h2>Our Team</h2>
                    <p>Behind Artjunks is a passionate team of art lovers, tech enthusiasts, and community builders. We come from diverse backgrounds but share a common goal: to create a thriving ecosystem for artists and art lovers alike. Our team works tirelessly to improve the platform, support our community, and push the boundaries of online art marketplaces.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <img src="/api/placeholder/400/200" alt="Community Impact" class="card-image">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h2>Community Impact</h2>
                    <p>At Artjunks, we believe in giving back. We regularly organize virtual art exhibitions, workshops, and charity auctions. A portion of our proceeds goes towards supporting art education initiatives and emerging artists from underrepresented communities. By choosing Artjunks, you're not just buying art â€“ you're contributing to a more vibrant and inclusive art world.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="cta-section">
            <h2>Join Our Community</h2>
            <p>Whether you're an artist looking to share your creations with the world, or an art lover searching for that perfect piece, Artjunks is your destination.</p>
            <a href="#" class="cta-button">Start exploring Artjunks today!</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function isElementInViewport(el) {
            const rect = el.getBoundingClientRect();
            return (
                rect.top >= 0 &&
                rect.left >= 0 &&
                rect.bottom <= (window.innerHeight || document.documentElement.clientHeight) &&
                rect.right <= (window.innerWidth || document.documentElement.clientWidth)
            );
        }

        function handleScroll() {
            const cards = document.querySelectorAll('.card');
            cards.forEach(card => {
                if (isElementInViewport(card)) {
                    card.style.opacity = '1';
                    card.style.transform = 'translateY(0)';
                }
            });
        }

        // Set initial styles
        document.querySelectorAll('.card').forEach(card => {
            card.style.opacity = '0';
            card.style.transform = 'translateY(20px)';
            card.style.transition = 'opacity 0.5s ease, transform 0.5s ease';
        });

        // Initial check on load
        handleScroll();

        // Check on scroll
        window.addEventListener('scroll', handleScroll);
    </script>
</body>
</html>